app: The new COVID-19 symptom self-check tool is now available on the University of Oregon mobile app. Download the app from the iTunes store or Google Play to access the symptom checker, campus map, and additional COVID-19 resources.
self_reporting: If you have tested positive or think you have been exposed to COVID-19, contact the Corona Corps Care Team at 541-346-2292 or coronacorps@uoregon.edu.
